  "remarks": "Alexey Vyaznikov is the General Director of JSC Central Research Institute “Elektron”, a Russian research and manufacturing company, which has won a government procurement contract for developing and producing high-tech electronic components for the Russian defence industry. Therefore, Alexey Nikolaevich Vyaznikov is supporting and benefitting from Russia’s military and industrial complex.",
